  <chunk id="c848bce30b9e60bccfd15a5534af1d0cea54c686.c5" text="Conclusions: This study of ICU patients in both China and US showed that thrombocytopenia is associated with an increased risk of ARDS and platelet count in combination with ARDS had a high predictive value for patient mortality.">
